Screen Emulator

Purpose: 
--------
This is a screen emulator and responsive design tool. It may be useful for web developers who need to test screen sizes.

Where:
------
The tool can be found at http://emitche.github.io/screenemulator.

Info:
-----
This app is currently under development.

Notes:
------
The app includes 3 responsive tools:
  1) Resizeable iframe utilizing jQuery UI (similar to changing the physical size of your browser by dragging the side)
  2) Mobile, tablet, and desktop views to-scale (when viewed on a laptop/desktop)
  3) Specify height and width

This app uses iframes. Some sites do not support displaying their site in an iframe for security reasons. 
  
